  </aside>
  <p>
        <idx><h>implicit functions</h><h>implicitplot!filledregions</h></idx> \begin{maplegroup} \begin{mapleinput} {implicitplot(L, x=-1.2..1.2, y=-1.2..1.8, coloring = ["red","blue"], filledregions=true); } <idx><h>implicit functions</h><h>implicitplot!colour</h></idx> \end{mapleinput} \relax \vskip.5\MaplePlotHeight Plot: tutorials/figures/Implicit_Functions_and_Graphsplot2d3-eps-converted-to.pdf\vskip.5\MaplePlotHeight \end{maplegroup}
  </p>
